{"tid":1669163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開] 尊重下啦香港人！","createTime":"2019-10-22T11:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T16:18:34.000Z","uid":127064,"like":95,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"10bacead039df2394404ea7e42acf31dc5eca731","tid":1669163,"uid":127064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T11:29:48.000Z","msg":"睇posts睇到要出下聲<br />\n發覺有啲香港人真係好以偏概全<br />\n<br />\n利申 中印mixed 中文唔太好 見諒<br />\n<br />\n首先<br />\n印度有好多種宗教 <br />\n大家聽得多既有Hinduism and Sikhism 而依兩個宗教係North part like Delhi and Mumbai係非常普及<br />\n<br />\n但要知埋印度人都信Catholicity and Christianity 而依兩個宗教就係South part such as Hyderabad and Kochi 比較普遍 <br />\n<br />\n當然 Islam都有但係印度比較少見 for example 佢地有啲住係有爭議性既地區 like Kashmir<br />\n<br />\n而至於你平時香港見到既印度人 其實可以係信以上五種任何一種 或者其他 什至唔信都得架！<br />\n唔好以為個個望落似印度人 就係Muslim 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 信islam既都可以係Pakistani and Bangladeshi 或者其他種族架！<br />\n<br />\n見到有人留言話 &ldquo;呀星&rdquo; 係Muslim 之類既野 做乜呀？？你地所講既 &ldquo;呀星&rdquo; 係Sikh 包頭的 佢地係唔會去Islam mosque架 唔好混埋一齊 <br />\n<br />\n仲有 唔好見到South East Asian looking 就一口咬定係邊到邊到人 係好唔尊重架！如果真係想了解就先問佢地既race係咩 講咩語言 etc Pakistani 好憎比人話係 Indian vice versa 你都唔想比人話係中國人啦係咪？<br />\n<br />\n雖然we connect咗 但都要尊重返呀！<br />\n好似有啲1999 希望睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命！"},{"pid":"83b01252d50a051eff07194fd8fc77e0db86d655","tid":1669163,"uid":201604,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T11:30:22.000Z","msg":"香港人真係冇乜sense"},{"pid":"541e2db111dc2f7a5325f896279c33dbae11d87a","tid":1669163,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T11:30:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3293029037f23e3165047a547ce73ab2319862a","tid":1669163,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T11:32:09.000Z","msg":"推！！！<br />\n不要無知"},{"pid":"28be8f8cb600624c2eb8bcd4f6ff2382bf16bcc6","tid":1669163,"uid":127064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid