\n<br />\n而至於你平時香港見到既印度人 其實可以係信以上五種任何一種 或者其他 什至唔信都得架！<br />\n唔好以為個個望落似印度人 就係Muslim 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 信islam既都可以係Pakistani and Bangladeshi 或者其他種族架！<br />\n<br />\n見到有人留言話 &ldquo;呀星&rdquo; 係Muslim 之類既野 做乜呀？？你地所講既 &ldquo;呀星&rdquo; 係Sikh 包頭的 佢地係唔會去Islam mosque架 唔好混埋一齊 <br />\n<br />\n仲有 唔好見到South East Asian looking 就一口咬定係邊到邊到人 係好唔尊重架！如果真係想了解就先問佢地既race係咩 講咩語言 etc Pakistani 好憎比人話係 Indian vice versa 你都唔想比人話係中國人啦係咪？<br />\n<br />\n雖然we connect咗 但都要尊重返呀！<br />\n好似有啲1999 希望睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:41:36.000Z","msg":"respect. 學野"},{"pid":"d6bfbf1a0ec278ba6e0558b81bc8cc5666b0e1a3","tid":1669163,"uid":254594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a864865a3a016373d69d4f72845ce2214dbfedee","tid":1669163,"uid":127064,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"de042302a743ea490a81795241bc0a916084f02b","tid":1669163,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d6a816c3defcf95259a7432825a155b07f8752df","tid":1669163,"uid":127064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T12:49:20.000Z","msg":"我冇講過 &ldquo;唔識=唔尊重&rdquo; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我只係話 &ldquo;尊重=主動識&rdquo; &amp; &ldquo;唔識=井底之蛙&rdquo; <br />\n依到係兩個concepts don&rsquo;t mix these two up<br />\n你唔識 頂多係井底之蛙 唔係唔尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T12:51:09.000Z","msg":"咁我唔主動識 又係咪唔尊重？<br />\n等睇你繼續詭辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:25:46.000Z","msg":"What a logical fallacy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOkay let&rsquo;s talk about this from the very beginning <br />\nIn my context: A=B and B=A which means if you choose to understand this matter proactively then you are being respectful. <br />\nBut with the way y